  "subject": "Fix: Use newer image for Ubuntu 22.04 Docker",
  "commit_message": "Fix: Use newer image for Ubuntu 22.04 Docker\n\nThere was an error while building the 20250424 image, or it was\nmanually built incorrectly. This change updates to the 20250623, which\nwas built properly for a docker image and has all associated software.\nFixes LF-Jira IT-28734\n\nChange-Id: I9945815c5e595b82f5658538528e82bed3923aae\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nSigned-off-by: Eric Ball <eball@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
